plications of our results for the detection of extreme-mass-ratio\ninspirals from galactic nuclei with a range of physical properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2011 20:56:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 May 2011 18:47:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-22"}
